sequenceDiagram
    participant Administrator
    participant StreamlitUI
    participant NLP_Parser
    participant Engine
    participant Optimizers
    participant Database

    Administrator->>StreamlitUI: Upload dataset and constraints
    StreamlitUI->>NLP_Parser: Parse constraints
    NLP_Parser-->>StreamlitUI: Parsed constraints JSON

    Administrator->>StreamlitUI: Generate Timetable
    StreamlitUI->>Engine: Generate initial timetable
    
    StreamlitUI->>Optimizers: Run GA, SA, and TS
    Optimizers-->>StreamlitUI: Return solutions
    
    StreamlitUI->>StreamlitUI: Select best solution
    StreamlitUI->>Database: Save timetable
    StreamlitUI-->>Administrator: Display schedule
